eringen har varslet en bemanningsnorm for barnehager innen 2020, men det er ikke kjent hva en slik norm vil inneb\u00e6re."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "fe7b4409d5670214fe25c14dbe97468ad6caef7dc372a0f32ca8afb3281a47c7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-06-12T17:16:12.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Hvis alle barn i Trondheim skal f\u00e5 barnehageplass den m\u00e5neden de fyller ett \u00e5r, vil det \u00f8ke kommunens utgifter med 202 millioner kroner \u00e5rlig."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article12879490.ece/p2g932/ALTERNATES/w980-default/AVVIK_1_2.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/174737ee9ab1738aa4d4c765c8987890d30b4b2e.jpg?59882154"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Flere barnehageopptak gir sjokkregning -adressa.no", "H\u00f8stbarna f\u00e5r plass", "Fortvilte foreldre", "Nasjonalt l\u00f8ft", "Flere ansatte"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "174737ee9ab1738aa4d4c765c8987890d30b4b2e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Barnehage", "Kunnskapsdepartementet", "Jon Gunnes", "Yngve Brox", "Eirik Schr\u00f8der", "Trondheim kommune"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Barnehage,Kunnskapsdepartementet,Jon Gunnes,Yngve Brox,Eirik Schr\u00f8der,Trondheim kommune"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": ["education", "law-government-and-politics"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barnehageplass", "barn f\u00f8dt", "barn", "barnehage", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kunnskapsdepartementet", "gran\u00e5senerkl\u00e6ringen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-per